data.title: Anna Q. Nilsson
data.meta_description: Sold for $148 | One of the very earliest actresses in film to achieve fame and the first Swedish actor to get a star on the Walk of Fame. Pretty vintage 9 x 12
data.text:
Description

One of the very earliest actresses in film to achieve fame and the first Swedish actor to get a star on the Walk of Fame. Pretty vintage 9 x 12 photo, signed and inscribed in green fountain pen “For Billy, Very good wishes, Sincerely, Anna Q. Nilsson.” Small tear and chip to top edge, and some scattered light silvering, otherwise fine condition. R&R COA.
